show.description: A battle-hardened soldier becomes the personal bodyguard of a beautiful, powerful CEO, protecting her from hidden dangers while uncovering deep conspiracies. As love sparks amid chaos, his strength and loyalty are tested against ruthless enemies and corporate intrigue. Watch "Me and My Sister" now!
